    person("Nippon Telegraph", "and Telephone Corporation", role = "cph")
  )
Maintainer: Akiru Kato <paithiov909@gmail.com>
Description: This package is a plain 'Rcpp' wrapper of 'MeCab', a CJK
    tokenizer and morphological analysis tool. The main goal of this
    package is to provide an alternative to 'tidytext' for CJK text data.
